com.riverbed.jsconapi.rest

Interface SconObjectAPI

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    SconAppAPI, SconNodeAPI, SconPathRulesAPI, SconPortAPI, SconSiteAPI, SconUplinkAPI, SconWanAPI, SconZoneAPI

    public interface SconObjectAPI
    This interfaces defines the primitives to create, update, get or delete any objects on SteelConnect.
    Version:
    1.0
    Author:
    rjourdan romain.jourdan@gmail.com

                            java.lang.String objectName,

        Returns a SconObject object based on its name
        Parameters:
        realmUrl - The URL of SteelConnect Realm in the following format "https://xyz.riverbed.cc"
        orgID - The id of the SteelConnect organization to make the call to. orgId will be in the following format "org-abc-xyz"
